OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774433137
OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FVets will be legally required to
OL,7,Fpublish their price lists and stick to
OL,8,Fprescription fee caps, the competition
OL,9,Fwatchdog has announced.
OL,11,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,12,F(CMA) said its reforms for the sector
OL,13,Fwill help pet owners better navigate
OL,14,Fthe vet services market.
OL,16,FOther legally binding measures will
OL,17,Finclude a price comparison website and
OL,18,Fmandatory branding by the large groups
OL,19,Fto help boost competition and drive
OL,20,Fdown prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
