OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774433137
OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FThe CMA said pet owners using a vet
OL,7,Fpractice that is part of a larger
OL,8,Fchain can expect to see changes before
OL,9,FChristmas, including standard price
OL,10,Flists.
OL,12,FThe measures follow the CMA finding
OL,13,Fthat fees have risen at almost twice
OL,14,Fthe rate of inflation, with pet owners
OL,15,Fnot being given enough information
OL,16,Fabout their vet and the prices of
OL,17,Ftreatments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
