FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774433137
OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FMartin Coleman, chairman of the
OL,7,Findependent Inquiry Group, said: "This
OL,8,Fis the most extensive review of
OL,9,Fveterinary services in a generation,
OL,10,Fand today's reforms will make a real
OL,11,Fdifference to the millions of pet
OL,12,Fowners who want the best for their
OL,13,Fpets but struggle to find the
OL,14,Fpractice, treatment and price that
OL,15,Fmeets their needs."
OL,17,FColeman added: "Too often, people are
OL,18,Fleft in the dark about who owns their
OL,19,Fpractice, treatment options and prices
OL,20,F` even when facing bills running into
OL,21,Fthousands of pounds."
OL,26,@oD@bOUyD@POU
