OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FWhen it comes to price lists, the CMA
OL,7,Fsaid practices must publish a
OL,8,Fcomprehensive list for standard
OL,9,Fservices, including consultations,
OL,10,Fcommon procedures, diagnostics,
OL,11,Fwritten prescriptions and cremation
OL,12,Foptions under its new rules.
OL,14,FPrescriptions, for which many
OL,15,Fpractices currently charge #30 or
OL,16,Fmore, are to be capped at #21 for the
OL,17,Ffirst medicine and #12.50 for any
OL,18,Fadditional medicines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
