OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FPractices must also provide a written
OL,7,Festimate in advance for any treatment
OL,8,Fexpected to cost #500 or more,
OL,9,Fincluding aftercare costs, as well as
OL,10,Fan itemised bill.
OL,12,FEmergency care will be the only
OL,13,Fexception for written estimates.
