OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FPrices and information about who owns
OL,7,Fthe surgery are to be made available
OL,8,Fto pet owners through the Royal
OL,9,FCollege of Veterinary Surgeons (RCVS)
OL,10,F'Find a Vet' service, which will share
OL,11,Fthe data with third-party comparison
OL,12,Fsites.
OL,14,FVet businesses must make it clear
OL,15,Fwhether they are part of a group or an
OL,16,Findependent business, with details of
OL,17,Fgroup ownership to be displayed on
OL,18,Fsigns at the surgery and online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
