OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FBritish Veterinary Association
OL,7,Fpresident Rob Williams said: "The
OL,8,Fmajority of the CMA's measures focus
OL,9,Fon increasing transparency and
OL,10,Finformation, which will help pet
OL,11,Fowners make more informed choices and
OL,12,Fsupport competition, which is a really
OL,13,Fpositive step."
