OL,3,CGreater transparency for pet owners as
OL,4,CUK vets forced to publish price lists
OL,6,FHe added: "Delivering highly skilled
OL,7,Fveterinary medicine is costly and
OL,8,Fwhilst we recognise prices have risen
OL,9,Fsharply in recent years this is due to
OL,10,Fa number of factors, including the
OL,11,Fhigher costs all businesses are
OL,12,Fexperiencing ` and vet practices are
OL,13,Fnot immune."
